targets.query: SELECT last(BOARDLOC) FROM "$quabo"  WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping'
SELECT last(PCBREV_N) FROM "$quabo" WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping'

panels.description:
Status timeline of this Quabo's various statuses.

Note that in a given module, only the Quabo at position 1 contains valid Shutter Status metadata.

targets.query: SELECT last("LIGHT_SENSOR_STATUS") FROM "$quabo" WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT last("SHUTTER_STATUS") FROM "$quabo" WHERE  "observatory" = '$observatory' AND $timeFilter AND BOARDLOC%4=1 GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT last("StartUp") FROM $quabo WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)

SELECT last("AGG_STATUS_MSG")
FROM $quabo
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter
GROUP BY time($__interval), "UID" fill(null)

SELECT last("AGG_STATUS_LEVEL")
FROM $quabo
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter
GROUP BY time($__interval), "UID" fill(null)

panels.title: Status timeline

panels.description:
"Detector x"  plots the current drawn by detector array x.

Please see https://github.com/panoseti/panoseti/issues/149 for details about how this value is computed from the raw detector current measurement, HVIMONx

targets.query:
SELECT HVIMON0 - (abs(HVMON0) / 0.499) / 1000000
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT HVIMON1 - (abs(HVMON1) / 0.499) / 1000000
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT HVIMON2 - (abs(HVMON2) / 0.499) / 1000000
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT HVIMON3 - (abs(HVMON3) / 0.499) / 1000000
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT DETR0_CURR
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT DETR1_CURR
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT DETR2_CURR
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter

SELECT DETR3_CURR
FROM "$quabo" 
WHERE "observatory" = '$observatory' AND "datatype"='housekeeping' AND $timeFilter
